Class DBMList

  • java.lang.Object
    • pta.Zone
      • pta.NCZone
        • pta.DBMList

  • public class DBMList
extends NCZone
    List of DBMs representing a non-convex zone. See this reference for some useful algorithms: S. Tripakis. The formal analysis of timed systems in practice. Joseph Fourier University, 1998.
